<zk xmlns:n="http://www.zkoss.org/2005/zk/native">
<n:h2>[ 1898649 ] The shading of Timebox should be the same with textbox</n:h2>
	<n:ol>
		<n:li>Check the timebox shadow and compare to textbox</n:li>
		<n:li>Also check the readonly, When readonly, you can only click (cannot type)</n:li>
		<n:li>Also check the disable, When disable, you cannot do anything</n:li>
	</n:ol>
<textbox/>
<timebox id="tb"/>
<button label="disable" onClick="tb.disabled = !tb.disabled"/>
<button label="readonly" onClick="tb.readonly = !tb.readonly"/>
</zk>
